data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home in Riverview, Florida! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house with a sparkling pool and a brand-new roof is a true gem. This home offers the perfect combination of comfort, style, and modern amenities. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan, with ample natural light streaming in through large windows. The spacious living area is perfect for family gatherings or entertaining friends, and it seamlessly flows into the dining area and kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space for all your culinary needs. It's the heart of the home, where you can whip up delicious meals and create lasting memories with loved ones. The master suite is a private oasis, complete with an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The three additional bedrooms are generously sized and offer plenty of room for family members or guests. The second bathroom is conveniently located to serve these bedrooms. Step outside to the screened lanai and pool area, where you can relax and unwind in your own tropical paradise. Enjoy the Florida sunshine, take a refreshing dip in the pool, or host cook outs. The fully fenced backyard provides added privacy and security. What sets this home apart is the brand-new roof, ensuring your peace of mind and protecting your investment. Other notable features of this property include a two-car garage, a laundry room, and easy access to nearby schools, shopping, and dining options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the Florida lifestyle at its finest. Your dream home at 9719 White Barn Way awaits!
